Configure WimpFont 0
If "<Wimp$Font>" = ""     Then Set Wimp$Font Homerton.Medium
If "<Wimp$FontSize>" = "" Then Set Wimp$FontSize 224
RMEnsure FontManager   3.41 RMLoad System:Modules.Fonts

| Ensure that the NCFresco options pages are pointing to those in STB3 ResourceFS
IfThere Resources:$.!Boot.HTML.Setup Then Set OptScr$Path Resources:$.!Boot.HTML.Setup.

RMReInit ShrinkWrap
ShrinkWrapAddZone Resources:$.Apps
Obey Resources:$.Apps.!ARMovie.!Boot
Obey Resources:$.Apps.!MovieFS.!Boot
Obey Resources:$.Apps.!CodecCtl.!Boot
Obey Resources:$.Apps.!NCKeybd.!Boot
Obey Resources:$.Apps.!Watchdog.!Boot

| If the ROM version of Macrovision is old, set defaults for newer (loaded) module to
| avoid screen shifting when we load the newer version
If "<Macrovision$RCV2EN>" = "" Then SetEval Macrovision$RCV2EN 0
If "<Macrovision$RCV2SN>" = "" Then SetEval Macrovision$RCV2SN 0

| Load a new version of the Macrovision module if the ROM version is too old
SetEval Macrovision$SoftLoading 0
RMEnsure Macrovision 0.26 SetEval Macrovision$SoftLoading 1
If Macrovision$SoftLoading Then RMLoad System:Modules.Macrovisio
If Macrovision$SoftLoading Then Unset Macrovision$RCV2*
Unset Macrovision$SoftLoading
RMEnsure Macrovision 0.26 Error "««PreSTB3_Macrovision»»"

| Uncomment to override default values for Macrovision on the next screen mode change
|SetEval Macrovision$RCV2E  1
|SetEval Macrovision$RCV2EN 57
|SetEval Macrovision$RCV2S  0
|SetEval Macrovision$RCV2SN 16

| Clear screen then run utility to load the new Interlace module
Echo <12>
RMEnsure Interlace 0.50 Run STBUtilities:InterLoad System:Modules.Interlr
